The TODO contains tasks we need to work on beside package commitments. These
tasks are high prioritized. If we manage to finish most of them we are able to
focus on 'package commitments', 'package updates' and 'automation' tasks!
So, pick up tasks from the following todo list and assign it to yourself. Also,
add your new ideas to the list so that we won't forget anything

Keep this list always up-to-date!
